    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Articles or physical resources used to array, dress up, rig out, equip, or otherwise provide with what is requisite for efficient action by a person or animal or for a thing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
